<div class="max-w-3xl md:mr-auto text-center md:text-left">
  <span class="eyebrow">Why DEVS exists</span>
  <h2 class="mt-5 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
    Built to close the school-to-team gap.
  </h2>
  <p class="mt-6 text-lg copy-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto md:mx-0 leading-relaxed">
    I'm a CS grad with 8+ years in the software industry and over 4 as a developer. The most important onboarding skills—PR flow, sprint planning, and review communication—were not taught clearly before my first developer job. DEVS is practical training for day-one confidence: build, ship, collaborate, and communicate like a professional teammate.
  </p>

  <!-- Compact founder strip -->
  <div class="mt-12 pt-10 border-t border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center sm:items-start gap-5 text-center sm:text-left">
    <img
      src="/images/josh-ahles.jpeg"
      alt="Josh Ahles, Founder of DEVS"
      class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl object-cover border border-[var(--color-border)] flex-shrink-0"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <div>
      <p class="font-semibold text-white">Josh Ahles</p>
      <p class="text-sm copy-subtle mt-0.5">CS grad • 8+ years in the software industry, over 4 as a developer</p>
      <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap justify-center sm:justify-start gap-2">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/joshahles/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface-0)]/70 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:border-[var(--color-accent)]/50 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 mr-1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4.98 3.5A2.48 2.48 0 1 0 5 8.46a2.48 2.48 0 0 0-.02-4.96ZM3 9h4v12H3V9Zm7 0h3.83v1.71h.05c.53-1 1.84-2.06 3.79-2.06C21.2 8.65 22 10.97 22 14v7h-4v-6.2c0-1.48-.03-3.38-2.06-3.38-2.06 0-2.37 1.61-2.37 3.27V21h-4V9Z"/></svg>
